name: Solar Scapes
description:
Your own randomly generated solar system, based off your wallet address (or randomized if you're UNSYNCED.) by @Rorscratch. Send me your solar systems on twitter, I want to see them!

Click and Drag to look around, click on planets to focus on them and listen to the music change.
Top left button displays wallet address, dice button randomizes the seed, and the reverse button puts you back on your seed if you randomized it.
